<emphasis box="[1291,1401,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">takaminei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by its indistinct metanotal groove, while distinct in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Terayama" authorityYear="1996" box="[710,851,260,285]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="takaminei">
<emphasis box="[710,724,261,284]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">P</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[741,851,260,285]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">takaminei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wheeler" authorityYear="1928" box="[868,1036,260,285]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scabra">
<emphasis box="[868,1036,260,285]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Ponera scabra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinct from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Terayama" authorityYear="1996" box="[1230,1362,260,285]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kohmoku">
<emphasis box="[1230,1244,261,284]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">P</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1261,1362,260,285]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">kohmoku</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by its small eyes consisting of 5–7 facets, but about 20 facets in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Terayama" authorityYear="1996" box="[804,933,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kohmoku">
<emphasis box="[804,818,297,320]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">P</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[832,933,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">kohmoku</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wheeler" authorityYear="1928" box="[947,1113,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scabra">
<emphasis box="[947,1113,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Ponera scabra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinct from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Terayama" authorityYear="1996" box="[1297,1435,295,320]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Ponera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="takaminei">
